# Hansim Design System: The Cheerful Engineer

## Core Principles

1. **No-Line Rule**: Never use 1px borders. Use background color shifts.
2. **Extreme Roundness**: Minimum 16px, prefer 32px+ (3rem).
3. **Soft Engineering**: Precise data + friendly UI.
4. **Light-Mode First**: Bright, welcoming experience.

## Essential Colors

```tsx
// Primary
bg-primary              // #006A35 - Logic Green
bg-primary-dim          // #005C2D - Gradient
bg-primary-container    // #6BFE9C - Highlight Glow

// Surfaces (Tonal Layering)
bg-surface                     // #F5F6F7 - Global
bg-surface-container-low       // #EFF1F2 - Zones
bg-surface-container-lowest    // #FFFFFF - Cards
bg-surface-container-high      // #E0E3E4 - Chips

// Text
text-on-surface          // #2C2F30 - NOT black
text-on-surface-variant  // #595C5D - Secondary
text-primary             // #006A35 - Accent
```

## Component Patterns

### Cards (No-Line Rule)

```tsx
// ✅ Correct
<div className="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-[3rem] no-line-boundary">

// ❌ Wrong
<div className="bg-white p-10 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
```

### Buttons

```tsx
// Primary CTA - Gradient + pill
<button className="px-10 py-5 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dim text-on-primary rounded-full font-extrabold hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all">

// Secondary
<button className="px-6 py-3 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors">
```

### Typography

```tsx
// Hero: text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter
// Section: text-2xl font-black tracking-tight
// Card: text-lg font-bold
// Meta: text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest
```

## Critical Rules

### ✅ Always Do

- Use `no-line-boundary` instead of `shadow-lg`
- Use `rounded-[3rem]` for major cards
- Use `toLocaleString()` for numbers (1,248 not 1248)
- Use `text-on-surface` (#2C2F30) not pure black
- Use gradient for primary CTAs: `bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dim`
- Apply `hover:scale-105` to interactive elements

### ❌ Never Do

- Never use `border` or `border-gray-*`
- Never use `rounded-sm` or `rounded-md` (too sharp)
- Never use `text-black` or `#000000`
- Never use flat `bg-primary` for buttons (use gradient)
- Never use `shadow-xl` or `shadow-2xl` (too harsh)

## Layout

### Max Width
```tsx
max-w-screen-2xl  // Home page
max-w-6xl         // Detail pages
max-w-4xl         // Leaderboard
max-w-3xl         // Search bar
```

### Spacing (4px Grid)
```tsx
gap-6    // 24px
p-8      // 32px
mb-10    // 40px
mb-24    // 96px
```

